    <p style="margin-top: 24px; padding: 18px 20px; background: #F8F9F4; border-left: 4px solid #3D4F2F; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Browse all <a href="/sports/" style="color: #3D4F2F; font-weight: 600;">Sports & Fitness gummies</a> — explore our complete category of expert-tested gummy guides for every supplement need in this space.</p>

