      <span class="key-stat-num">68%</span>
      <p class="key-stat-txt">of Create creatine gummy customers are women. <strong>Female creatine adoption grew 340% between 2021 and 2025</strong>, driven by emerging research on cognitive and bone-density benefits, social media education debunking the "bulky" myth, and the availability of gummy formats that eliminate the gym-bro aesthetic of powder and shaker bottles.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- WOMEN-SPECIFIC BENEFITS -->
